WEBVTT

00:08.341 --> 00:09.501
Report.

00:09.576 --> 00:11.407
A ship just de-cloaked
off our port stern.

00:11.478 --> 00:12.775
Can you identify them?

00:12.846 --> 00:14.279
They re-cloaked.

00:15.415 --> 00:16.939
That disruptor blast

00:17.017 --> 00:18.245
had a Klingon signature.

00:19.352 --> 00:20.944
Evasive maneuvers.

00:21.054 --> 00:22.112
Hail them.

00:23.189 --> 00:24.747
No response.

00:31.731 --> 00:33.926
Port shields
are down to 50 percent.

00:35.235 --> 00:36.065
They've re-cloaked again.

00:36.169 --> 00:37.898
The tetryon readings indicate

00:38.004 --> 00:39.596
it's a D7-class cruiser.

00:39.706 --> 00:43.506
D7? They were
retired decades ago.

00:43.576 --> 00:45.510
lf their technology
is antiquated...

00:45.578 --> 00:46.670
Perhaps a metaphasic

00:46.746 --> 00:47.610
scan might be able

00:47.680 --> 00:49.580
to penetrate their cloak.

00:49.649 --> 00:50.616
Do it.

00:50.683 --> 00:52.548
Bridge to Astrometrics.

00:52.619 --> 00:55.087
lnitiate a metaphasic sweep.

00:57.390 --> 00:59.017
l've detected a vessel.

00:59.159 --> 01:01.889
Transferring the trajectory
to Tactical.

01:01.995 --> 01:03.553
l have them.

01:03.630 --> 01:05.427
Fire phasers.

01:11.371 --> 01:13.066
Our cloak has failed.

01:13.173 --> 01:16.939
Divert emergency power
to shields.

01:17.010 --> 01:19.240
Forward emitters are off-line.

01:19.312 --> 01:22.372
The Federation ship
is hailing again.

01:22.449 --> 01:23.643
Answer them.

01:23.716 --> 01:24.944
Captain!

01:25.085 --> 01:26.245
lt may give us more time

01:26.319 --> 01:28.219
to get the cloak
back on line. Visual.

01:29.556 --> 01:31.524
This is Captain Kathryn Janeway

01:31.591 --> 01:33.616
of the Federation
Starship Voyager.

01:33.693 --> 01:34.785
Stand down.

01:34.861 --> 01:37.056
We will not surrender
to sworn enemies

01:37.130 --> 01:38.495
of the Klingon Empire.

